  "description": "Highlights: • Family friendly resort with water slides • Access to 8 à la carte restaurants (unlimited visits) • Family friendly rooms • State-of-the-art meeting rooms • Access to neighboring sister hotel Remal Beach Resort In the middle of Sharm El Sheikh’s scenic landscape and mountains, SUNRISE Remal Resort is an intimate oasis for comfort. The 335 family- friendly rooms at Remal Resort offer all the comfort you need for an unforgettable family vacation at the Red Sea. Every room comes with satellite TV, air conditioning, minibar with soft drinks, tea & coffee making facilities and much more. Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the resort and in all rooms. The resort offers an all- inclusive dine around experience. Enjoy culinary delights in the international restaurant with a daily changing theme buffet or dine at one of the 8 renovated à-la-carte restaurants serving Steak, Egyptian, Mexican, Mediterranean, Indian & Thai cuisine. For seafood lovers, the Resort hosts a Seafood à-la-carte restaurant (chargeable). There is a 24-hour lobby bar, beach & pool bars. It features a fully equipped gym (16+), and a full-serviced spa & beauty salon (chargeable). The large pool area with slides is set to keep you splashing at all times. For those seeking for a tranquil escape, guests have access to a private sandy beach on Ras Nasrani’s beautiful sea. The SUNRISE Kid’s Club led by professional care takers is available for kids between 3-12 years old offering Daily Educational, Entertaining Sports & Activities. Located 10 minutes from Neama Bay City Centre and Sharm El Sheikh International Airport, the hotel offers the perfect balance between desert privacy and exploring the city’s nightlife. Our all-inclusive concept includes: Breakfast, Lunch and Dinner in Buffets or a la carte Restaurants (unlimited reservations), Snacks from 12:00-17:00, 22:30-01:00, local alcoholic Beverages from 10:00-00:00, Water and Hot Beverages 24/7, Minibar with water and soft drinks, Wi-Fi, free entertainment and sports activities, and much more. Some activities/services such as Diving Center, Spa Treatment are extra charge.",
